message.content:
You are a senior frontend engineer reviewing a pull request. Review the following changes for task L03450: "Create global styles (src/styles/global.scss)".

The task requirements:
- Reset defaults, apply dark theme background, set font family
- Set box-sizing border-box, remove margins/padding
- Import tokens
- Style scrollbars to match Raycast (thin, subtle, webkit-scrollbar 6px, track transparent, thumb rgba white 0.15)
- Style ::selection with accent color
- Set -webkit-font-smoothing antialiased
- Set base font size and line height

Project rules:
- Bun runtime, TypeScript strict, React 19, Vite 6, Sass
- No CSS modules, no styled-components, no tailwind
- No comments in code unless JSDoc needed
- File naming: snake_case

FILES CHANGED:

1. src/styles/global.scss (NEW FILE):
```scss
@use 'tokens' as *;

*,
*::before,
*::after {
  box-sizing: border-box;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

html {
  font-size: $font-md;
  line-height: 1.5;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
}

body {
  font-family: $font-family;
  background-color: $color-background;
  color: $color-text-primary;
}

::selection {
  background-color: $color-accent;
  color: $color-text-primary;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar {
  width: 6px;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
  background: transparent;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  border-radius: 3px;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
}
```

2. src/main.tsx (MODIFIED - added import):
```tsx
import { StrictMode } from 'react';
import { createRoot } from 'react-dom/client';
import { App } from './App';
import './styles/global.scss';

const root = document.getElementById('root');

if (!root) {
  throw new Error('Root element not found');
}

createRoot(root).render(
  <StrictMode>
    <App />
  </StrictMode>,
);
```

3. Existing tokens file (src/styles/_tokens.scss) for reference:
```scss
$color-background: #1a1a1c;
$color-surface: #262628;
$color-surface-hover: #2e2e30;
$color-border: #3a3a3c;
$color-text-primary: #f5f5f7;
$color-text-secondary: #98989d;
$color-text-tertiary: #6e6e73;
$color-accent: #007aff;
$color-accent-hover: #0a84ff;
$color-destructive: #ff453a;

$space-1: 4px;
$space-2: 8px;
... (standard spacing scale)

$font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Text', 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
$font-xs: 11px;
$font-sm: 12px;
$font-md: 13px;
$font-lg: 15px;
$font-xl: 20px;

$transition-fast: 80ms;
$transition-normal: 150ms;
$transition-slow: 250ms;
```

Please review:
1. Does it meet ALL the task requirements?
2. Are there any bugs or issues?
3. Does it follow project conventions?
4. Any improvements needed?

Be specific and actionable in feedback. If everything looks good, say so clearly.

